{"comments":"Interactive State System for Brand Compounds.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nEvery interactive component has multiple states. Each state can specify\ndifferent visual properties, animations, haptics, and sounds. States\ncompose to define the complete interactive experience.\n\n## State Categories\n\n- **Interactive**: hover, active, focus, disabled\n- **Validation**: valid, invalid, pending\n- **Loading**: loading, success, error\n- **Selection**: selected, checked, indeterminate\n\n## At Billion-Agent Scale\n\nState transitions must be deterministic. Given the same input state\nand event, all agents must compute the same output state. This module\ndefines the state vocabulary; resolution happens at render time.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[97,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brand/Compound/State.purs","start":[97,3]},"title":"StateDefault"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[98,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brand/Compound/State.purs","start":[98,3]},"title":"StateHover"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[99,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brand/Compound/State.purs","start":[99,3]},"title":"StateActive"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[100,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brand/Compound/State.purs","start":[100,3]},"title":"StateFocus"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[101,22],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brand/Compound/State.purs","start":[101,3]},"title":"StateFocusVisible"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[102,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brand/Compound/State.purs","start":[102,3]},"title"